parameters: Oh, it's Laura. What are you doing here? Are you lost?

\SE[16]Oh, the Spirit of the Wind...!!? \!\SE[12]Why are you
in a place like this...?

Why...? This place is my hometown. I came here for a 'Fairy
Obon' to visit my family. You know, sometimes you have to
show your face.

Ah, I see. You're lost, right? It happens occasionally. I
can use my power to take you back to your original place, if
you'd like?

Is there something so rare...? Well, if you ever want to go
back, just let me know anytime.

Huh, are you done with your business? Shall I use my power
to send you back to your original place?

Is there something so rare...? Well, if you ever want to go
back, just let me know anytime.
It seems like an artificial fairy child....

Ah, that's an Imaginary Baby! Recently, the marriage rate
has been significantly declining, so it has become popular
as a substitute plaything.

Nowadays, getting married is too old- fashioned.... It's a
big gamble to take such a risk, so I'd rather not. We have
to manage the risk like this.

\SE[29]... Y-Yeah, that's right. There are various thoughts,
aren't there...
